# =========================================
# VEDA Official Example 05
# Title: Personal Profile
# Concepts: ask, say, Smart Output
# Difficulty: Beginner
# =========================================

ask name: Enter your name:
ask age: Enter your age:
ask city: Enter your city:

say:
say: ===== YOUR PROFILE =====
say: Name : {name}
say: Age  : {age}
say: City : {city}
say: ========================